data.description: Look no further. This three-bedroom, two-bathroom home is ideal for a growing family or as a potential investment. This home is situated in a community recognized for its tranquility and rurality, Buckingham. Country living that is nevertheless conveniently close to the city.  This house welcomes you with a spacious, open concept design that offers lots of room for customization. Creating a family room, dining area, and living room is all up to you. Situated on one side of the home, the master bedroom is spacious and equipped with a sitting tub for your comfort. This home also features a large lanai space that is perfect for an outdoor living area with access to a spacious backyard. Don't pass on this chance to obtain a piece of Buckingham. Contact us to arrange your viewing. This house is easy to show and can be scheduled for appointments on short notice.
